123
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:04,120
Ready?

124
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:06,559
Spin.

125
00:13:06,560 --> 00:13:08,280
Spin, spin, spin, spin, spin.

126
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:12,360
Spin, spin, spin again.

127
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:15,480
Another spin, spin, spin, spin.

128
00:13:16,040 --> 00:13:17,040
This angle.

129
00:13:17,680 --> 00:13:18,680
Down here.

130
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,280
There.

131
00:13:22,520 --> 00:13:23,520
Teh,

132
00:13:23,800 --> 00:13:24,920
