awake all night, Mr. Toh?

182
00:18:51,200 --> 00:18:55,400
Oh, I heard someone…
maybe your brother, called you earlier.

183
00:18:55,800 --> 00:18:56,800
Ah.

184
00:18:57,560 --> 00:18:59,200
Yes, that was my brother.

185
00:18:59,720 --> 00:19:00,840
I'm Doctor Freeze.

186
00:19:01,120 --> 00:19:02,120
Oh,

187
00:19:02,600 --> 00:19:03,600
