188
00:19:03,720 --> 00:19:04,960
You can just call me P'Freeze.

189
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:06,720
Sure.

190
00:19:07,080 --> 00:19:08,600
You can just call me Toh.

191
00:19:09,480 --> 00:19:11,160
So, you're a doctor?

192
00:19:11,600 --> 00:19:15,200
