195
00:19:26,520 --> 00:19:28,640
You're talented. It's so cute.

196
00:19:29,280 --> 00:19:32,759
Yes, I planned to draw for every customer.

197
00:19:32,760 --> 00:19:35,760
But since it's my first day,
It's been a bit chaotic.

198
00:19:36,520 --> 00:19:39,760
So yours is the very first one I've done.

199
00:19:40,280 --> 00:19:43,120
Wow, I'm honored then.

200
00:19:43,480 --> 00:19:45,000
And the coffee's excellent.

201
00:19:45,680 --> 00:19:47,040
Thank you.

202
00:19:47,480 --> 00:19:49,360
Please let me know if
you have any feedback.

203
00:19:49,560 --> 00:19:51,120
Of course.

204
00:19:51,800 --> 00:19:55,720
Mr, Toh, we're almost out of ice.
How do I order more?

205
00:19:56,106 --> 00:19:58,619
I think I wrote the number down somewhere.

206
00:19:59,440 --> 00:20:01,320
Please excuse me, Mr. Freeze.

207
00:20:01,560 --> 00:20:02,800
Take your time.

208
00:20:30,040 --> 00:20:31,320
Have a seat.

209
00:20:51,760 --> 00:20:53,160
Right here?

210
00:20:56,080 --> 00:20:59,400
But I like it… it's exciting.

211
00:21:31,440 --> 00:21:33,000
Bank,

212
00:21:36,680 --> 00:21:38,600
