220
00:22:28,920 --> 00:22:33,480
If Mama begs me, I'm
ready to take him back.

221
00:22:39,720 --> 00:22:41,920
Are you saying it's my fault?

222
00:22:43,960 --> 00:22:45,680
Listen to me.

223
00:22:46,480 --> 00:22:50,400
I'm never wrong. I never beg anyone first.

224
00:22:59,520 --> 00:23:01,120
You're my son.

225
00:23:01,880 --> 00:23:04,160
You must be on my side.

226
00:24:00,800 --> 00:24:02,360
