230
00:24:13,480 --> 00:24:16,120
Don't worry, I'll buy some for you.

231
00:24:17,560 --> 00:24:20,280
Recently, you only love Saensee, huh?

232
00:24:22,960 --> 00:24:26,480
I must love the boy as well as his Papa.

233
00:24:32,680 --> 00:24:34,040
I don't believe you.

234
00:24:40,040 --> 00:24:41,680
I don't believe you.

235
00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:51,640
I still don't believe you.

236
00:24:56,120 --> 00:24:57,120
