237
00:25:03,040 --> 00:25:04,080
No.

238
00:25:07,480 --> 00:25:08,480
Believe me.

239
00:25:08,560 --> 00:25:09,560
You win.

240
00:25:12,040 --> 00:25:13,440
This is a bonus.

241
00:25:17,953 --> 00:25:21,953
If I want to stop the pain, I must end it.

242
00:25:27,600 --> 00:25:30,520
I'm sorry, Saensee.

243
00:26:22,960 --> 00:26:26,640
P'Toh is such a magnet.
Did you see those customers today?

244
00:26:26,840 --> 00:26:29,360
The guy who bumped into him this morning.

245
00:26:29,520 --> 00:26:32,199
He was top-tier.

246
00:26:32,200 --> 00:26:38,080
He looked so warm,
friendly, and sophisticated.

247
00:26:39,680 --> 00:26:41,080
Must be that four-eyes.

248
00:26:43,080 --> 00:26:44,640
What should I do?

249
00:27:05,800 --> 00:27:09,960
Oh, Toh. One of my patients gave me
a bunch of these art exhibition flyers.

250
00:27:10,280 --> 00:27:12,360
